---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Lost in the garden" description="404 — this page does not exist (yet).">
  <section class="py-16 text-center">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-4">404</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif leading-tight mb-4">
      迷路了 / Lost in the garden
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[color:var(--color-muted)] max-w-prose mx-auto mb-8">
      这片土壤里还没有种过这棵植物。也许它曾在这里、已被移走，或者从未存在。<br />
      <span class="block mt-2">This patch of soil hasn't grown that plant — yet.</span>
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 text-sm">
      <a href="/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-[color:var(--color-border)] hover:bg-[color:var(--color-border)] no-underline">
        ← Home
      </a>
      <a href="/garden/" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md border border-[color:var(--color-border)] hover:bg-[color:var(--color-border)] no-underline">
        Browse the garden
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
